# Cards

## Installation & Import

```bash
yarn add @ids-ts/cards
```

```tsx
import { Cards } from '@ids-ts/cards';
```

## Props

### Card

| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| `size` | `'standard' \| 'small' \| 'xsmall'` | No | Card size variant. Defaults to `'standard'`. |
| `onClick` | `MouseEventHandler` | No | Click handler for the card. |
| `disableCardClick` | `boolean` | No | When true, disables the card click interaction. |
| `automationId` | `string` | No | Test automation identifier. |
| `style` | `CSSProperties` | No | Inline style overrides. |

### Sub-components

- `CardContent` — Wraps the main card content
- `CardActions` — Footer area for buttons and links
- `CardUpperControl` — Top-right control area (CloseIconControl, EditIconControl, etc.)
- `CardProgressBarIndicator` — Progress bar at the bottom of a card

