## Usage Patterns

### Basic Usage

```tsx
() => {
  const cardStyle = { margin: '10px' };

  return (
    <div style={{ display: 'flex', boxSizing: 'border-box' }}>
      <Card
        automationId="Cards_basic_example_standard"
        size="standard"
        style={cardStyle}
        onClick={action('standard card clicked')}
      >
        <CardContent>
          Basic example: <code className={styles.code}>standard</code>
        </CardContent>
      </Card>
      <Card
        automationId="Cards_basic_example_small"
        size="small"
        style={cardStyle}
        onClick={action('small card clicked')}
      >
        <CardContent>
          Basic example: <code className={styles.code}>small</code>
        </CardContent>
      </Card>
      <Card
        automationId="Cards_basic_example_xsmall"
        size="xsmall"
        style={cardStyle}
        onClick={action('xsmall card clicked')}
      >
        <CardContent>
          Basic example: <code className={styles.code}>xsmall</code>
        </CardContent>
      </Card>
      <br />
      <Card
        automationId="Cards_basic_example_fit_content"
        style={{ height: 'auto', width: '200px', ...cardStyle }}
        onClick={action('xsmall card clicked')}
      >
        <CardContent>
          This example is to fit content.
          <br />
          <br />
          Please see the API for details on how to replicate this.
          <br />
          <br />
          Just as a note, this is not yet a supported option for the
          &quot;size&quot; prop.
          <br />
          <br />
          We will be working on supporting this for the future grid system.
          <br />
          <br />
          You can pass in `height: &apos;auto&apos;` to accomplish this.
        </CardContent>
      </Card>
    </div>
  );
}
```

### Disable Click Card Example

```tsx
() => {
  const cardStyle = { margin: '0 15px' };

  return (
    <div style={{ display: 'flex', boxSizing: 'border-box' }}>
      <Card
        disableCardClick
        automationId="Cards_disable_click"
        size="standard"
        style={cardStyle}
      >
        <CardContent>Some content here</CardContent>
        <CardActions>
          <Link href="https://google.com">google.com</Link>
        </CardActions>
      </Card>
      <Card disableCardClick size="standard" style={cardStyle}>
        <CardContent>Some content here</CardContent>
        <CardActions>
          <Button purpose="standard">Check it out</Button>
        </CardActions>
      </Card>
      <Card disableCardClick size="standard" style={cardStyle}>
        <CardContent>
          <CardUpperControl action={<CloseIconControl />} />
          Some content here
        </CardContent>
      </Card>
    </div>
  );
}
```

